msg: Moved the code used for map projection initialisation in a separated Initializer class (package private).
Opportunistically use more double-double arithmetic. While the digits modified by this extra-precision are
not significant, the intend is not to increase map projection accuracy but rather to improve the result of
concatenations of MathTransforms (through an attempt to improve the result of matrix multiplications and inversions).
